			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				FYI, I recently had an issue where my Specialization:Alteration skill would not go past 50. I solved the problem by putting a practice into each of the other Specializations skills. My skill went to 51 on the next cast! Since having a 50 in each of the others is a good idea, this may be why not everyone experiences this issue. Hope this helps others!<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

