				Necros have a hard choice when it comes to specialization Alteration, Conjuration and Evocation can all be good choices.  The choice has to go to your style of play but I hear Alteration is usually the preferred with Conjuration second and Evocation third.  Again any of the 3 will probably work just fine for you. you still get specialization in the magics just not gonna be to a level as the one magic you choose. (not as much mana knocked off or may fizzle a little more.) 
